item.description:
Join me for a benefit for House Rabbit Network. They are a 501c non-profit who rescue rabbits from overcrowded kill shelters, captures stray domesticated rabbits that people toss out into the wild and educate owners to spay and neuter rabbits to prevent overpopulation. It's a great organization.

Rock Out for Rabbits!

Cover Charge of $5.00 will go to House Rabbit Network

Time Friday, July 29 at 8:00pm - July 30 at 12:00am

Location The Jam Factory 1211 Elm Street Manchester, NH

More Info 21+, $5 suggested donation. 100% of the door sales goes to HRN!! Come rock out to some local music and support HRN at the same time!

Featuring:

Tuna Fish Discrepancy

Mostly from Manchester, NH, Tuna Fish Discrepancy is a rock quartet with tongue planted firmly in cheek. Formed by Ross Boyd a while ago, TFD has transformed from four-track bedroom experimentation, to an acoustic duo with delusions of grandeur, to what is now a full fledged, “professional” band.

http://tunafishdiscrepancy.com/

The Fitted Shirt
